WEBVTT

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.940
=About Love=

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.940
=Episode 22=

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:30.000
Why are you here?

00:01:35.590 --> 00:01:37.560
Do you know who Lin Chen is with?

00:01:37.920 --> 00:01:39.790
Stay out of Lin Chen's business.

00:01:39.920 --> 00:01:41.920
He can be with whoever he wants now.

00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:43.840
You should spend this time

00:01:44.150 --> 00:01:45.430
focusing on your own work.

00:01:46.070 --> 00:01:47.150
By the way,

00:01:47.870 --> 00:01:49.560
today is

00:01:49.790 --> 00:01:50.710
a big day for me.

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:52.230
After I get it done,

00:01:52.300 --> 00:01:53.640
I'll call you tonight.
Let's celebrate.

00:01:53.840 --> 00:01:56.120
Don't tell me you're getting married?

00:01:57.680 --> 00:01:58.640
To Li Xiaoxi?

00:01:58.870 --> 00:01:59.870
Who else would it be?

00:02:02.020 --> 00:02:03.590
Do you know what kind of person she is?

00:02:06.280 --> 00:02:07.640
What are you gonna say now?

00:02:08.120 --> 00:02:09.560
She's a liar.

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:12.240
That lousy flower shop of hers
is just a front.

00:02:12.240 --> 00:02:13.120
Do you know that?

00:02:13.430 --> 00:02:15.310
She makes a living by seducing men.

00:02:15.310 --> 00:02:17.030
Alright, I already know all that.

00:02:18.470 --> 00:02:19.710
You know everything?

00:02:20.430 --> 00:02:22.240
Xiaoxi already told me everything.

00:02:24.080 --> 00:02:24.920
I know it all.

00:02:26.430 --> 00:02:27.270
An Miu,

00:02:27.800 --> 00:02:29.280
you're my closest friend.

00:02:29.630 --> 00:02:31.190
Can you stop opposing her?

00:02:31.400 --> 00:02:32.560
We're about to get married.

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:44.080
But do you know

00:02:44.470 --> 00:02:46.630
she's still seducing other men?

00:02:51.590 --> 00:02:52.430
What?

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:55.840
I told you. She's a total fraud!

00:02:56.870 --> 00:02:58.590
Do you know
what she does behind your back?

00:02:58.590 --> 00:02:59.750
Do you really know?

00:02:59.930 --> 00:03:01.360
Today you're getting married to her.

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:02.430
Guess what she's doing right now?

00:03:02.840 --> 00:03:05.470
She plays the innocent
and you actually believe it, man?

00:03:05.470 --> 00:03:06.800
Are you stupid?

00:03:07.280 --> 00:03:08.630
This is her signature trick!

00:03:08.630 --> 00:03:09.750
Alright, enough!

00:03:30.560 --> 00:03:32.520
I think you should think carefully.

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:35.750
She's honestly not right for you.

00:04:51.870 --> 00:04:54.480
I... I wanted to
cover you with a blanket.

00:04:54.480 --> 00:04:56.720
You were sleeping so soundly,
so I didn't wake you.

00:04:57.270 --> 00:04:58.110
Thanks.

00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:04.510
How much did I drink?

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:07.120
A lot. All the alcohol is finished.

00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:10.920
Not as much as your Du Mian though.

00:05:12.240 --> 00:05:13.430
Even he was done for.

00:05:20.870 --> 00:05:21.710
Thanks.

00:05:32.600 --> 00:05:34.160
Can I ask you something?

00:05:36.390 --> 00:05:37.430
What is it?

00:05:38.240 --> 00:05:39.720
Your ex-girlfriend.

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:41.510
Yeah, Zhen.

00:05:42.870 --> 00:05:44.120
You were together so long.

00:05:44.120 --> 00:05:45.190
Why did you break up?

00:05:50.360 --> 00:05:51.270
Sorry.

00:05:51.270 --> 00:05:52.680
Am I being too nosy?

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:54.520
Not.

00:05:56.120 --> 00:05:57.560
Didn't I tell you before?

00:05:58.510 --> 00:06:00.800
When she was running her business,

00:06:01.900 --> 00:06:03.430
she got scammed for a huge sum of money.

00:06:03.430 --> 00:06:04.270
She ended up in huge debt.

00:06:06.040 --> 00:06:07.190
That's when

00:06:08.480 --> 00:06:10.120
a man gave her a ton of money.

00:06:12.630 --> 00:06:13.470
Bye bye.

00:06:16.750 --> 00:06:18.560
Did he know you two were together?

00:06:21.270 --> 00:06:22.110
He did.

00:06:23.070 --> 00:06:23.920
But he didn't mind.

00:06:25.140 --> 00:06:26.480
He'd liked Zhen for a long time,

00:06:26.480 --> 00:06:27.430
and chased her for ages.

00:06:28.830 --> 00:06:30.950
Finally got his chance

00:06:33.160 --> 00:06:34.310
when I was at my lowest.

00:06:36.920 --> 00:06:38.310
What kind of person is that?

00:06:38.680 --> 00:06:39.920
So vicious.

00:06:40.870 --> 00:06:42.750
Pretending to be a hero

00:06:42.750 --> 00:06:43.830
coming to the rescue.

00:06:44.510 --> 00:06:46.000
Thinks he's some kind of savior?

00:06:47.750 --> 00:06:49.750
You talk a good game,

00:06:51.310 --> 00:06:52.390
but thanks for

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:54.510
comforting me and sticking up for me.

00:06:55.070 --> 00:06:56.630
I'll get revenge for you someday.

00:06:56.820 --> 00:06:58.240
Some people think tests

00:06:58.480 --> 00:07:00.370
can measure love's loyalty,

00:07:00.560 --> 00:07:01.400
you know?

00:07:02.510 --> 00:07:03.350
What do you mean?

00:07:03.750 --> 00:07:05.830
Like getting pretty girls

00:07:05.830 --> 00:07:07.480
to hit on men in different ways.

00:07:08.070 --> 00:07:09.920
Ninety-nine percent fall for it.

00:07:11.240 --> 00:07:12.870
Fake guys like Lin Chen

00:07:12.870 --> 00:07:14.240
will definitely show his true colors.

00:07:14.950 --> 00:07:15.920
I have to find proof.

00:07:16.120 --> 00:07:17.870
Let the past stay in the past.

00:07:18.360 --> 00:07:19.240
I don't care anymore.

00:07:19.680 --> 00:07:20.720
I have a girlfriend now.

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:22.600
I still feel it's unfair for you.

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:24.680
Did you forget I promised to

00:07:24.680 --> 00:07:25.680
stand up for you?

00:07:30.560 --> 00:07:31.480
Miss An,

00:07:31.630 --> 00:07:33.800
what's your relationship with Mr. Lin?

00:07:34.630 --> 00:07:36.000
Are you his fiancée

00:07:36.160 --> 00:07:37.040
or his girlfriend?

00:07:39.190 --> 00:07:41.600
I'm here on behalf of a friend.

00:07:42.680 --> 00:07:44.310
We don't accept

00:07:44.600 --> 00:07:46.800
indirect commissions
with unclear motives.

00:07:47.310 --> 00:07:48.830
The motive is clear.

00:07:49.060 --> 00:07:49.920
I just want to expose

00:07:49.920 --> 00:07:51.480
Lin Chen's true colors.

00:07:52.680 --> 00:07:53.630
He's a liar.

00:07:53.970 --> 00:07:54.830
Sorry,

00:07:54.830 --> 00:07:56.630
I really can't help you.

00:07:56.630 --> 00:07:57.470
Please, you should go.

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:01.310
Did I say something wrong?

00:08:02.390 --> 00:08:05.040
You wanting revenge on Lin Chen,

00:08:05.040 --> 00:08:06.000
that's your business.

00:08:06.600 --> 00:08:07.440
We

00:08:08.120 --> 00:08:10.190
only help vulnerable women here.

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:12.000
Trust me.

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:13.870
I am helping a woman right now.

00:08:14.190 --> 00:08:15.430
This guy isn't a good person.

00:08:15.920 --> 00:08:17.750
If trusting someone were that easy,

00:08:18.560 --> 00:08:19.750
you wouldn't be here, right?

00:08:20.120 --> 00:08:22.240
So what do I have to do for you
to help me?

00:08:24.400 --> 00:08:25.680
Sorry, I need to take this call.

00:08:26.420 --> 00:08:27.860
(Bei)

00:08:30.670 --> 00:08:31.900
Hello, Bei.

00:08:33.720 --> 00:08:35.270
Tomorrow works.

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:39.840
Can't I just call her Li Xiaoxi?

00:08:41.320 --> 00:08:43.320
Alright, I'll call her Sister.

00:08:43.320 --> 00:08:44.160
Happy now?

00:08:47.720 --> 00:08:48.910
That's it, bye bye.

00:08:52.960 --> 00:08:53.800
Sorry about that.

00:08:54.150 --> 00:08:55.000
So tell me

00:08:55.480 --> 00:08:57.270
why do you want to test Lin Chen?

00:08:57.840 --> 00:08:59.510
What's his relationship
with your friend?

00:09:02.600 --> 00:09:04.030
He's a hypocrite.

00:09:04.790 --> 00:09:06.270
He hurt the person I cared about most.

00:09:13.860 --> 00:09:14.700
(Voice Call)

00:09:15.060 --> 00:09:16.980
(Guan)

00:09:18.960 --> 00:09:19.800
Miss An.

00:09:20.400 --> 00:09:21.390
Did you get it on camera?

00:09:22.150 --> 00:09:24.000
Li Xiaoxi was sent by you, right?

00:09:24.390 --> 00:09:25.230
Yeah.

00:09:25.910 --> 00:09:27.080
Did you know everything?

00:09:28.080 --> 00:09:28.920
Of course.

00:09:29.200 --> 00:09:30.790
I wouldn't have sent her otherwise.

00:09:31.270 --> 00:09:32.790
What are you really up to?

00:09:33.270 --> 00:09:35.360
What I'm up to doesn't matter.

00:09:36.270 --> 00:09:37.550
Isn't this what you wanted?

00:09:38.030 --> 00:09:39.720
The current and the ex

00:09:39.910 --> 00:09:41.000
fell for the same trick.

00:09:41.550 --> 00:09:42.630
You have no competition now.

00:09:45.030 --> 00:09:45.910
Miss An.

00:09:46.480 --> 00:09:47.720
Sometimes love

00:09:48.120 --> 00:09:49.550
needs decisive action.

00:09:59.840 --> 00:10:00.750
Sis, you're here.

00:10:22.840 --> 00:10:23.680
Sis.

00:10:24.670 --> 00:10:26.120
Bei went out.

00:10:26.550 --> 00:10:27.510
Where did he go?

00:10:27.510 --> 00:10:28.350
I don't know,

00:10:28.630 --> 00:10:30.200
but he seemed really hurried.

00:10:30.720 --> 00:10:32.390
And didn't look too well.

00:10:54.060 --> 00:10:55.180
(Bei)

00:11:05.700 --> 00:11:08.460
(Li Xiaoxi)

00:11:16.630 --> 00:11:18.240
Hello, sir. Do you have an appointment?

00:11:18.450 --> 00:11:19.390
(Lin Chen)
Is Lin Chen here?

00:11:19.550 --> 00:11:21.840
(Senior Counseling Psychologist, Lin Chen)
Sorry, Dr. Lin is busy now.

00:11:21.840 --> 00:11:22.960
Shall I help you

00:11:22.960 --> 00:11:23.800
book an appointment first?

00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:26.320
Sir.

00:11:26.320 --> 00:11:28.380
(Lin Chen
Psychological Counseling Center)

00:11:33.150 --> 00:11:34.510
Sir, Sir, you're

00:11:34.510 --> 00:11:35.960
disturbing other clients, Sir.

00:11:38.270 --> 00:11:39.150
Sir.

00:11:39.150 --> 00:11:39.990
You...

00:11:40.870 --> 00:11:41.750
You really can't...

00:11:42.240 --> 00:11:44.030
You really can't
go any further inside, Sir.

00:11:45.720 --> 00:11:47.390
Sir, you... you can't do this, Sir.

00:11:48.080 --> 00:11:49.790
Sir! Sir! Sir!

00:11:50.150 --> 00:11:51.240
Sir, you can't do that, Sir!

00:11:51.240 --> 00:11:52.080
Sir!

00:12:06.440 --> 00:12:07.280
Excuse me.

00:12:10.000 --> 00:12:10.840
Bei!

00:12:19.300 --> 00:12:20.140
(Police)

00:12:25.060 --> 00:12:26.660
(Jiang Yifan)

00:12:39.600 --> 00:12:42.360
Hey, Jiang Yifan, what's up?

00:12:42.670 --> 00:12:43.720
Bei's in trouble.

00:12:45.200 --> 00:12:46.480
Oh? Huh?

00:12:49.740 --> 00:12:51.390
Don't tell me
he got into a car accident?

00:12:51.390 --> 00:12:52.720
No, he beat someone up.

00:12:52.720 --> 00:12:54.030
He's at the police station now.

00:12:56.120 --> 00:12:57.440
That doesn't make sense.

00:12:57.870 --> 00:12:59.720
He's the rational
little angel of justice.

00:12:59.720 --> 00:13:00.960
How could he be so impulsive?

00:13:01.100 --> 00:13:02.200
Who could push him that far?

00:13:02.510 --> 00:13:03.720
Can't explain in a few words.

00:13:04.320 --> 00:13:05.270
Hurry over.

00:13:05.900 --> 00:13:07.120
I'll send you the location later.

00:13:07.480 --> 00:13:08.320
Okay.

00:13:13.910 --> 00:13:15.840
Yeah, Qingping Police Station
on Huanhua Street.

00:13:17.120 --> 00:13:18.910
Don't get lost, hurry.

00:13:19.360 --> 00:13:21.440
What happened?
How'd he get into a fight?

00:13:21.600 --> 00:13:23.030
Did someone drunk start trouble?

00:13:23.270 --> 00:13:25.270
Bei beat someone up.

00:13:25.480 --> 00:13:26.440
What? What the hell?

00:13:26.870 --> 00:13:28.030
Why'd he do that?

00:13:28.200 --> 00:13:29.630
Gong, were you at the scene?

00:13:29.910 --> 00:13:31.360
No, I wasn't. I've got no idea.

00:13:31.360 --> 00:13:32.200
Hurry over!

00:13:32.840 --> 00:13:34.270
Do we need a lawyer?

00:13:34.910 --> 00:13:36.100
(Legal Mediation)
Go ahead.

00:13:36.120 --> 00:13:37.120
Who threw the first punch?

00:13:40.790 --> 00:13:41.630
Me.

00:13:43.030 --> 00:13:43.910
Why did you hit him?

00:13:45.080 --> 00:13:47.390
(Host: Police Office)
On the serious side, fighting

00:13:47.670 --> 00:13:48.960
is a criminal offense.

00:13:50.290 --> 00:13:51.790
Severe cases can lead to imprisonment.

00:13:55.550 --> 00:13:56.630
It's not really fighting.

00:13:57.550 --> 00:13:59.000
We're old friends.

00:13:59.220 --> 00:14:00.360
We've known each other for years.

00:14:00.360 --> 00:14:01.840
Just messing around.

00:14:02.360 --> 00:14:03.720
Then it got a bit out of hand.

00:14:03.910 --> 00:14:05.320
Messing around like this?

00:14:05.720 --> 00:14:07.200
Now you're scared?

00:14:07.510 --> 00:14:09.720
Since we were called
and brought you here,

00:14:10.270 --> 00:14:11.510
do you think you can

00:14:11.510 --> 00:14:13.000
brush it off with a few words?

00:14:13.000 --> 00:14:13.840
Is that possible?

00:14:14.200 --> 00:14:15.040
No.

00:14:15.100 --> 00:14:16.150
I didn't mean it that way.

00:14:18.600 --> 00:14:19.670
Is what he said true?

00:14:23.240 --> 00:14:24.440
We really didn't fight.

00:14:26.480 --> 00:14:27.910
I just wanted to punch him.

00:14:32.390 --> 00:14:33.550
Did you fight back just now?

00:14:36.330 --> 00:14:38.120
I couldn't just stand there
and take it, right?

00:14:38.320 --> 00:14:39.510
Did you fight back just now?

00:14:39.510 --> 00:14:40.670
Just answer. Did you fight back?

00:14:42.510 --> 00:14:43.550
Yes, I did. I fought back.

00:14:48.000 --> 00:14:48.840
Well,

00:14:50.550 --> 00:14:51.790
my head hurts.

00:14:53.000 --> 00:14:54.670
Maybe you should take me
to the hospital.

00:14:54.670 --> 00:14:55.960
I think it's pretty bad.

00:14:58.630 --> 00:14:59.480
(Police)
Everything okay?

00:14:59.480 --> 00:15:00.550
How's Bei doing?

00:15:00.550 --> 00:15:01.960
What happened? Why'd he fight?

00:15:05.080 --> 00:15:05.920
Who'd he hit?

00:15:06.120 --> 00:15:07.000
Is the injury bad?

00:15:07.980 --> 00:15:09.150
No idea. They won't let me in.

00:15:09.150 --> 00:15:10.080
Just told me to wait here.

00:15:10.670 --> 00:15:11.510
Officer.

00:15:11.960 --> 00:15:14.270
My friend got into a little scuffle.

00:15:14.750 --> 00:15:16.720
He's inside, right?

00:15:18.440 --> 00:15:19.550
The two who were fighting?

00:15:19.550 --> 00:15:20.440
Yeah.

00:15:20.440 --> 00:15:21.510
I already told you.

00:15:21.570 --> 00:15:22.510
They're taking statements.

00:15:22.650 --> 00:15:24.480
Family will be notified
once there's a result.

00:15:26.840 --> 00:15:28.670
Officer, sorry for the trouble.

00:15:29.440 --> 00:15:31.600
But one of them is my fiancé.

00:15:31.700 --> 00:15:33.030
Can I go in and say a word to him?

00:15:33.320 --> 00:15:35.320
Sorry, I understand how you feel.

00:15:35.320 --> 00:15:37.030
But no one's allowed to see him now.

00:15:38.870 --> 00:15:40.630
Then can we ask

00:15:41.030 --> 00:15:43.630
how this is usually handled?

00:15:44.510 --> 00:15:46.910
First, we see how serious it is.

00:15:47.120 --> 00:15:48.910
For one-sided attacks like this,

00:15:49.440 --> 00:15:51.270
it depends on the victim's injuries.

00:15:51.270 --> 00:15:53.440
If it's minor, we'll mediate.

00:15:53.600 --> 00:15:55.390
If they agree to settle
and compensate actively,

00:15:55.390 --> 00:15:56.230
it'll be fine.

00:15:57.790 --> 00:15:58.720
Well...

00:15:59.200 --> 00:16:00.600
what if they don't agree to settle?

00:16:00.910 --> 00:16:02.080
Then it's hard to say.

00:16:02.440 --> 00:16:04.270
According to
public security regulations,

00:16:04.550 --> 00:16:06.000
detention for five to ten days
at minimum.

00:16:06.150 --> 00:16:07.720
Severe cases lead to imprisonment.

00:16:08.390 --> 00:16:09.230
Imprisonment?

00:16:11.600 --> 00:16:12.440
Oh my god.

00:16:13.510 --> 00:16:14.580
- Bei!
- Bei.

00:16:15.240 --> 00:16:17.200
The settlement paperwork's done.

00:16:17.550 --> 00:16:18.630
You can go now.

00:16:26.000 --> 00:16:27.030
Thank you, officer.

00:16:27.030 --> 00:16:28.320
Sorry for troubling you so late.

00:16:28.400 --> 00:16:30.120
No need to thank me.
This comrade

00:16:30.750 --> 00:16:31.960
decided not to press charges.

00:16:34.670 --> 00:16:36.080
I just want this over with.

00:16:36.100 --> 00:16:37.320
I still need to go to the hospital.

00:16:42.790 --> 00:16:43.960
She's your girlfriend?

00:16:49.440 --> 00:16:50.440
Got it.

00:16:51.480 --> 00:16:53.200
Were we both set up?

00:16:54.390 --> 00:16:55.720
Dude, you're pretty jacked.

00:16:55.720 --> 00:16:56.560
What?

00:16:58.100 --> 00:16:59.360
Your arms are pretty big, right?

00:16:59.360 --> 00:17:00.200
Forty-two centimeters?

00:17:00.630 --> 00:17:01.630
Where do you work out?

00:17:01.790 --> 00:17:02.750
Bei, are you hurt?

00:17:02.910 --> 00:17:03.790
Need to go to the hospital?

00:17:07.510 --> 00:17:08.350
Let's go home.

00:17:13.340 --> 00:17:16.860
(Police)

00:17:16.880 --> 00:17:17.720
How's it going?

00:17:22.510 --> 00:17:23.510
How are you?

00:17:23.920 --> 00:17:25.240
Why are you so badly hurt?

00:17:35.680 --> 00:17:37.750
I'm fine,
seeing you makes the pain go away.

00:17:39.110 --> 00:17:39.960
You're already like this

00:17:39.960 --> 00:17:41.160
and still in the mood to joke.

00:17:42.160 --> 00:17:43.000
Take it slow.

00:18:24.590 --> 00:18:25.430
Get in the car.

00:18:31.400 --> 00:18:32.830
Where are you two going?

00:18:33.960 --> 00:18:35.590
What? Another plan?

00:18:37.240 --> 00:18:38.240
Yeah.

00:18:38.400 --> 00:18:39.240
You go first.

00:18:39.880 --> 00:18:40.750
Alright, we're off.

00:18:45.240 --> 00:18:46.790
Let's go get a drink?

00:18:46.790 --> 00:18:47.920
Okay.

00:18:47.920 --> 00:18:48.760
Then it's on you.

00:18:49.960 --> 00:18:51.160
Look at you, acting all coy.

00:18:52.500 --> 00:18:53.390
Let's split it evenly.

00:19:11.880 --> 00:19:12.720
You okay?

00:19:22.030 --> 00:19:23.350
I have someone I like,

00:19:23.680 --> 00:19:24.640
but

00:19:24.640 --> 00:19:26.200
she's never been my girlfriend.

00:20:05.700 --> 00:20:06.790
I'll get the first-aid kit.

00:20:38.400 --> 00:20:39.240
Does it hurt?

00:20:58.200 --> 00:20:59.640
About those photos,

00:21:04.510 --> 00:21:05.880
can you let me explain?

00:21:14.550 --> 00:21:16.550
If I said we were set up,

00:21:19.920 --> 00:21:20.760
would you believe me?

00:21:24.440 --> 00:21:26.550
My old partner, Guan.

00:21:27.000 --> 00:21:27.840
You've met her too.

00:21:29.160 --> 00:21:30.790
She's been trying to get me back.

00:21:32.000 --> 00:21:33.200
She also called those guys

00:21:33.200 --> 00:21:34.160
who fought at Linglong.

00:21:35.310 --> 00:21:36.200
This time she told me

00:21:36.200 --> 00:21:37.510
her sister has a terminal illness.

00:21:38.830 --> 00:21:40.640
She wants her fiancé to leave her.

00:21:42.900 --> 00:21:43.840
That fiancé is Lin Chen.

00:21:50.270 --> 00:21:51.640
I couldn't refuse

00:21:51.640 --> 00:21:53.070
a request

00:21:53.070 --> 00:21:54.400
from a girl facing death.

00:21:56.640 --> 00:21:57.480
But...

00:21:59.070 --> 00:22:00.270
But I never thought

00:22:01.270 --> 00:22:02.720
it was all a lie,

00:22:05.270 --> 00:22:06.480
a trap of hers.

00:22:12.550 --> 00:22:14.030
I don't even know why she

00:22:15.310 --> 00:22:16.750
would go to so much trouble

00:22:16.750 --> 00:22:17.830
to do this.

00:22:35.480 --> 00:22:37.400
If I'd told you before

00:22:37.400 --> 00:22:38.310
I met Lin Chen,

00:22:40.480 --> 00:22:41.350
would you not

00:22:41.350 --> 00:22:42.720
be so mad?

00:22:53.750 --> 00:22:54.750
It's my fault.

00:22:59.310 --> 00:23:01.030
Maybe it was wrong from the start.

00:23:06.350 --> 00:23:08.400
I care too much what you think of me.

00:23:10.600 --> 00:23:13.190
♪I'll admit♪

00:23:15.400 --> 00:23:16.790
Let's not talk about this today.

00:23:19.510 --> 00:23:20.830
My head's a mess.

00:23:24.550 --> 00:23:25.390
Well,

00:23:27.360 --> 00:23:28.590
I'll stay at the shop for a few days.

00:23:29.480 --> 00:23:30.590
I just need some quiet.

00:23:34.080 --> 00:23:37.430
♪There's no one that
I wouldn't try to fool♪

00:23:37.760 --> 00:23:41.330
♪For an image of you♪

00:23:42.230 --> 00:23:44.110
♪Take my hand again♪

00:23:44.680 --> 00:23:46.160
If you don't want to see me,

00:23:48.830 --> 00:23:50.000
I can go home for a few days..

00:23:50.200 --> 00:23:51.040
No need.

00:23:52.080 --> 00:23:54.190
♪I'm on my knees again♪

00:23:55.270 --> 00:23:56.680
Too much happened today.

00:23:58.750 --> 00:24:00.240
I need to think,

00:24:01.640 --> 00:24:02.680
process it all.

00:24:05.310 --> 00:24:06.830
I just want a quiet time alone.

00:24:11.110 --> 00:24:11.950
Is that okay?

00:24:12.440 --> 00:24:15.830
♪Did it come from above♪

00:24:15.920 --> 00:24:19.290
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:24:19.400 --> 00:24:24.410
♪Is it a push or a shove♪

00:24:24.860 --> 00:24:27.150
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

00:24:27.170 --> 00:24:32.100
♪This secret of love♪

00:24:32.740 --> 00:24:34.140
♪I'm addicted♪

00:24:34.940 --> 00:24:38.260
♪Every second of the day♪

00:24:40.260 --> 00:24:43.700
♪Walking round the corners
of the room♪

00:24:44.140 --> 00:24:48.020
♪Chasing your shadows♪

00:24:48.060 --> 00:24:50.100
♪When the curtains close♪

00:24:50.140 --> 00:24:52.140
♪I'll still be loving you♪

00:24:52.180 --> 00:24:55.340
♪Sinking deep and deeper again♪

00:24:56.100 --> 00:24:57.980
♪When the oceans fall♪

00:24:58.020 --> 00:24:59.860
♪I'll still be holding you♪

00:24:59.860 --> 00:25:03.540
♪Cause you are my truth♪

00:25:03.580 --> 00:25:07.580
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:25:07.620 --> 00:25:12.340
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:25:12.980 --> 00:25:16.060
♪I thought it had came from
below us♪

00:25:16.100 --> 00:25:19.540
♪Did it come from above♪

00:25:19.580 --> 00:25:23.380
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:25:23.420 --> 00:25:28.390
♪Is it a push or a shove♪

00:25:28.910 --> 00:25:31.900
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

00:25:31.940 --> 00:25:36.460
♪This secret of love♪

00:25:55.240 --> 00:25:56.790
Did I ever offend you somehow?

00:26:00.350 --> 00:26:02.110
Sit down, have some tea.

00:26:02.440 --> 00:26:04.720
You've worked hard
to make things this messy.

00:26:05.750 --> 00:26:07.310
Looks like the grudges run deep.

00:26:09.440 --> 00:26:11.160
Say whatever you have to my face.

00:26:12.270 --> 00:26:13.110
You forgot

00:26:17.270 --> 00:26:18.350
Cheng Yu?

00:26:20.680 --> 00:26:21.520
Xiaoxi,

00:26:22.640 --> 00:26:23.590
I think...

00:26:24.030 --> 00:26:25.240
Lately, Cheng Yu

00:26:25.960 --> 00:26:26.800
has been

00:26:28.000 --> 00:26:30.160
acting weird lately.

00:26:30.830 --> 00:26:32.680
Why don't you test him for me?

00:26:35.000 --> 00:26:36.750
I've always wanted to ask.

00:26:37.640 --> 00:26:39.510
Have we met somewhere before?

00:26:41.070 --> 00:26:42.720
We've known each other for a long time.

00:26:43.830 --> 00:26:45.160
But you definitely don't know me.

00:26:47.510 --> 00:26:48.960
Back in college,

00:26:48.960 --> 00:26:50.680
I took your public lecture.

00:26:51.440 --> 00:26:52.310
Professor Cheng.

00:26:53.920 --> 00:26:54.960
School of Natural Sciences.

00:26:56.170 --> 00:26:57.110
Which year were you in?

00:26:57.270 --> 00:26:59.270
The International Business Department,
Class of 2012.

00:27:01.350 --> 00:27:03.400
Now you're selling wine.

00:27:03.620 --> 00:27:04.920
It's quite a fit for your major.

00:27:05.310 --> 00:27:07.200
When did you get into
the red wine business?

00:27:07.830 --> 00:27:09.440
You've done so well.

00:27:10.440 --> 00:27:12.000
Makes me, a business major,

00:27:12.000 --> 00:27:13.400
feel totally outclassed.

00:27:21.620 --> 00:27:22.640
No matter how well it does,

00:27:23.300 --> 00:27:24.480
it has nothing to do with me.

00:27:25.880 --> 00:27:28.000
Professor Cheng,
is something on your mind?

00:27:29.440 --> 00:27:30.280
If you...

00:27:31.480 --> 00:27:32.550
if your

00:27:33.000 --> 00:27:33.920
life and

00:27:34.110 --> 00:27:35.270
every move you make

00:27:35.960 --> 00:27:37.590
are all planned out by someone else,

00:27:38.160 --> 00:27:39.720
no room for you to fight back,

00:27:40.030 --> 00:27:40.960
to say a word against it,

00:27:42.510 --> 00:27:43.590
you just have to take it.

00:27:43.750 --> 00:27:44.640
Would you be happy?

00:27:46.960 --> 00:27:47.880
Of course not.

00:27:49.720 --> 00:27:51.310
But I can't imagine

00:27:51.880 --> 00:27:53.720
anyone planning your life

00:27:54.830 --> 00:27:56.110
when you're in your position.

00:27:59.400 --> 00:28:00.240
I can't figure it out.

00:28:02.550 --> 00:28:03.440
Professor Cheng.

00:28:04.680 --> 00:28:06.510
Are you talking about...

00:28:11.480 --> 00:28:13.590
I never thought someone like you,

00:28:14.030 --> 00:28:16.640
who chases
independent spirit and free thinking,

00:28:17.880 --> 00:28:20.480
would be trapped by love
for 20 whole years.

00:28:27.160 --> 00:28:28.000
I think

00:28:29.270 --> 00:28:31.000
love itself is beautiful.

00:28:32.110 --> 00:28:34.550
But when two people are together,

00:28:35.200 --> 00:28:36.200
if people's

00:28:36.200 --> 00:28:37.720
status and wealth

00:28:37.880 --> 00:28:38.880
keep growing,

00:28:39.200 --> 00:28:40.200
their urge to control

00:28:40.750 --> 00:28:41.880
will grow too.

00:28:42.750 --> 00:28:43.750
It'll reshape you,

00:28:44.480 --> 00:28:45.510
and turn you into

00:28:45.510 --> 00:28:47.350
a total egomaniac.

00:28:48.200 --> 00:28:49.200
That's terrifying.

00:28:49.880 --> 00:28:50.790
Can you understand?

00:28:53.160 --> 00:28:54.000
I do.

00:28:57.590 --> 00:28:58.590
Sorry, Professor Cheng.

00:28:58.590 --> 00:29:00.830
I'm really happy to meet you today.

00:29:02.720 --> 00:29:04.110
Since we're getting along so well,

00:29:05.310 --> 00:29:06.510
how about going somewhere else

00:29:06.960 --> 00:29:08.160
to chat after dinner?

00:29:11.720 --> 00:29:12.560
I thought

00:29:13.350 --> 00:29:14.960
a great girl like you

00:29:15.790 --> 00:29:17.000
wouldn't be...

00:29:17.680 --> 00:29:18.520
Sorry.

00:29:19.160 --> 00:29:20.030
A casual person.

00:29:29.510 --> 00:29:30.510
Sorry, Professor Cheng.

00:29:30.650 --> 00:29:31.640
I have to take this call.

00:29:38.720 --> 00:29:39.560
Xiaoxi,

00:29:40.070 --> 00:29:40.910
how's it going?

00:29:42.110 --> 00:29:43.680
Cheng Yu's more cautious than I thought.

00:29:45.440 --> 00:29:46.280
I see.

00:29:47.440 --> 00:29:48.590
Give me a little more time.

00:29:48.790 --> 00:29:49.790
I think he's interested,

00:29:49.960 --> 00:29:50.880
just testing the waters.

00:29:51.510 --> 00:29:52.350
Forget it.

00:29:52.790 --> 00:29:53.630
That's enough.

00:29:54.070 --> 00:29:55.590
Thank you,
you've worked hard.

00:30:07.000 --> 00:30:08.640
Sorry to keep you waiting,
Professor Cheng.

00:30:10.920 --> 00:30:13.270
Time flew by while we talked.

00:30:15.000 --> 00:30:15.960
It's already this late.

00:30:16.270 --> 00:30:17.440
We really hit it off.

00:30:18.400 --> 00:30:19.440
I never thought

00:30:19.880 --> 00:30:20.920
I'd tell you all this.

00:30:22.720 --> 00:30:23.960
If we get a chance next time,

00:30:24.240 --> 00:30:26.550
you have to show me
your treasured Luce wine.

00:30:26.880 --> 00:30:27.720
Of course.

00:30:27.920 --> 00:30:30.750
Good wine is meant to be shared
with those who appreciate it.

00:30:38.750 --> 00:30:39.590
I'm sorry.

00:30:39.880 --> 00:30:40.720
Waiter!

00:30:41.440 --> 00:30:42.550
It's fine. It's okay.

00:30:42.680 --> 00:30:43.520
Here.

00:30:45.440 --> 00:30:46.590
Here, clean this up.

00:30:47.160 --> 00:30:48.070
Come, take a look.

00:30:52.510 --> 00:30:53.350
Sorry.

00:30:54.640 --> 00:30:55.480
It's okay.

00:30:57.440 --> 00:30:58.480
Well, Professor Cheng,

00:30:58.960 --> 00:31:00.160
I'll head out for today.

00:31:03.480 --> 00:31:04.640
Leaving so soon?

00:31:08.880 --> 00:31:09.790
Didn't you say

00:31:10.200 --> 00:31:11.310
you wanted to come to my house

00:31:11.510 --> 00:31:12.550
to see my Luce?

00:31:15.310 --> 00:31:16.400
It's too late today.

00:31:17.160 --> 00:31:18.510
Why don't we make it tomorrow?

00:31:19.030 --> 00:31:20.000
This bottle

00:31:20.350 --> 00:31:21.830
has been at my house for a long time.

00:31:23.720 --> 00:31:24.560
I want to open it

00:31:24.880 --> 00:31:25.920
for you tonight.

00:31:28.790 --> 00:31:29.630
Meeting you

00:31:29.960 --> 00:31:31.030
makes me feel like

00:31:31.030 --> 00:31:33.400
I'm young again.

00:31:37.000 --> 00:31:37.840
With you here,

00:31:38.880 --> 00:31:40.110
nothing else matters.

00:31:54.830 --> 00:31:55.670
Okay.

00:31:57.270 --> 00:31:58.920
I'll go with your plan, Professor Cheng.

00:32:34.500 --> 00:32:36.140
(Omnidirectional recording)

00:33:04.000 --> 00:33:04.920
Professor Cheng.

00:33:05.440 --> 00:33:06.920
You called me to your house.

00:33:08.270 --> 00:33:09.960
Do you have something to say to me?

00:33:31.110 --> 00:33:33.070
You two are just unlucky.

00:33:33.440 --> 00:33:34.920
My husband's not home.

00:33:34.920 --> 00:33:36.550
Otherwise, he'd cook you a great meal.

00:33:38.640 --> 00:33:41.240
Guan, your family life's so happy.

00:33:41.240 --> 00:33:43.110
No wonder you have no worries.

00:33:43.110 --> 00:33:45.550
You can put all your focus into work.

00:33:45.920 --> 00:33:47.400
I can't even be jealous of that.

00:33:47.590 --> 00:33:49.240
Today I want to see

00:33:49.510 --> 00:33:52.030
the jewels in your safe, Guan.

00:33:52.160 --> 00:33:53.350
I'm too excited.

00:33:53.590 --> 00:33:54.430
Sure.

00:34:09.070 --> 00:34:10.230
Guan.

00:34:10.230 --> 00:34:11.370
We have something to do.

00:34:11.380 --> 00:34:12.260
We'll come by next time.

00:34:12.260 --> 00:34:13.720
Yeah, yeah. We'll leave now.

00:34:20.960 --> 00:34:21.960
What are you two doing?

00:34:29.960 --> 00:34:30.840
You go out first

00:34:31.590 --> 00:34:32.670
I need to talk to him.

00:34:56.960 --> 00:34:57.880
What do you mean?

00:35:04.230 --> 00:35:05.070
You saw everything.

00:35:06.230 --> 00:35:07.150
Jerk!

00:35:07.760 --> 00:35:09.190
Total jerk!

00:35:20.150 --> 00:35:20.990
Let's break up.

00:35:29.880 --> 00:35:30.960
Leave me,

00:35:31.880 --> 00:35:34.280
and you'll be
a worthless penniless nobody.

00:35:34.280 --> 00:35:36.320
I don't care.
I can give up everything.

00:35:42.030 --> 00:35:43.070
Just for her?

00:35:44.440 --> 00:35:46.070
Yes, just for her.

00:36:08.920 --> 00:36:10.320
I want to explain.

00:36:11.030 --> 00:36:12.000
My phone broke that day.

00:36:12.000 --> 00:36:13.360
I couldn't reach you.

00:36:14.360 --> 00:36:15.360
I thought coming to his house,

00:36:15.360 --> 00:36:16.800
he'd say something.

00:36:17.070 --> 00:36:18.630
I could record solid evidence.

00:36:19.900 --> 00:36:21.230
But I didn't expect to run into you

00:36:21.230 --> 00:36:22.280
and your friend.

00:36:22.670 --> 00:36:23.800
He's gone now.

00:36:24.510 --> 00:36:26.030
The evidence doesn't matter anymore.

00:36:27.030 --> 00:36:27.870
Guan.

00:36:28.670 --> 00:36:29.550
Are you okay?

00:36:32.000 --> 00:36:33.190
It's just a man.

00:36:33.480 --> 00:36:34.590
No big deal.

00:36:35.960 --> 00:36:36.800
You can leave now.

00:36:37.960 --> 00:36:38.800
Alright.

00:36:40.360 --> 00:36:41.200
I'll leave now.

00:36:41.440 --> 00:36:42.280
Mm.

00:37:09.230 --> 00:37:10.590
Do you believe in karma?

00:37:12.400 --> 00:37:14.510
If it's not a coincidence,

00:37:14.670 --> 00:37:16.440
then maybe it's fate's plan.

00:37:17.670 --> 00:37:18.510
One day,

00:37:19.360 --> 00:37:21.920
you'll love someone with all your heart.

00:37:22.840 --> 00:37:24.110
That's when I'll get the chance

00:37:24.440 --> 00:37:25.510
to test

00:37:26.070 --> 00:37:27.230
if your true love

00:37:27.630 --> 00:37:29.320
is really perfect.

00:37:31.190 --> 00:37:32.190
You're doing this to me

00:37:32.550 --> 00:37:34.840
just because
I laid the truth out in front of you?

00:37:37.030 --> 00:37:37.870
Truth?

00:37:38.710 --> 00:37:39.920
What truth?

00:37:41.320 --> 00:37:42.800
Even if your phone broke,

00:37:43.190 --> 00:37:45.190
you had a thousand chances

00:37:45.480 --> 00:37:46.960
to call it off with Cheng Yu.

00:37:47.590 --> 00:37:48.430
But you didn't.

00:37:48.930 --> 00:37:50.000
You just had to keep going.

00:37:51.550 --> 00:37:52.550
You had to

00:37:53.550 --> 00:37:55.000
shove everything in my face.

00:37:56.030 --> 00:37:57.320
You forced my head down,

00:37:57.590 --> 00:37:58.800
made me watch it all,

00:38:01.280 --> 00:38:02.590
and made me have to accept it.

00:38:07.880 --> 00:38:08.720
I never thought...

00:38:11.190 --> 00:38:12.920
I never thought you'd think this way.

00:38:15.360 --> 00:38:16.710
Then how do you expect me to think?

00:38:18.000 --> 00:38:19.670
Aren't you so proud?

00:38:20.300 --> 00:38:21.510
The satisfaction of stepping on

00:38:21.760 --> 00:38:24.070
every man under your feet.

00:38:25.360 --> 00:38:26.200
Cheng Yu and I...

00:38:27.670 --> 00:38:28.510
20 years.

00:38:30.030 --> 00:38:31.030
20 years.

00:38:32.800 --> 00:38:34.630
Do you know how hard it was
to get here?

00:38:34.630 --> 00:38:35.470
You know?

00:38:46.550 --> 00:38:48.110
When we first came to this city,

00:38:49.110 --> 00:38:51.000
we had nothing.

00:38:52.710 --> 00:38:53.550
But we had each other

00:38:54.000 --> 00:38:55.030
in our hearts.

00:38:56.510 --> 00:38:58.710
I worked day and night

00:38:59.480 --> 00:39:00.320
at a beauty salon.

00:39:01.110 --> 00:39:02.360
The first money I earned,

00:39:03.590 --> 00:39:04.880
I bought him a luxury watch.

00:39:06.800 --> 00:39:08.280
Seeing it on his wrist

00:39:08.570 --> 00:39:09.630
and seeing his satisfaction

00:39:10.760 --> 00:39:12.070
made me so happy.

00:39:13.230 --> 00:39:14.070
And

00:39:14.440 --> 00:39:15.430
he'd buy the most expensive,

00:39:16.030 --> 00:39:17.150
and tastiest food from school

00:39:17.320 --> 00:39:19.760
every day for me.

00:39:21.030 --> 00:39:22.760
Rode his beat-up bike

00:39:23.230 --> 00:39:24.320
from East City

00:39:24.760 --> 00:39:25.960
to West City

00:39:26.230 --> 00:39:27.360
to bring it to me.

00:39:27.760 --> 00:39:29.030
Stayed to watch me eat,

00:39:32.510 --> 00:39:33.350
while he

00:39:35.030 --> 00:39:37.030
only had steamed buns and pickles.

00:39:40.400 --> 00:39:41.320
That kind of love.

00:39:42.400 --> 00:39:43.240
Can you get it?

00:39:50.230 --> 00:39:52.360
Now... 20 years.

00:39:53.360 --> 00:39:55.510
20 years has all become a joke.

00:40:01.070 --> 00:40:03.480
Every time I close my eyes,

00:40:04.440 --> 00:40:06.030
I see you hugging him,

00:40:06.360 --> 00:40:07.440
and him holding you.

00:40:08.840 --> 00:40:10.630
He was saying those heartless words.

00:40:11.920 --> 00:40:13.230
I keep having nightmares.

00:40:13.920 --> 00:40:15.110
I don't even want to sleep.

00:40:15.400 --> 00:40:17.280
Every night I dream you're together.

00:40:23.440 --> 00:40:25.920
So you want me to feel the same pain.

00:40:27.710 --> 00:40:28.550
You never know

00:40:30.110 --> 00:40:31.670
until

00:40:33.630 --> 00:40:34.800
you've been there.

00:40:38.000 --> 00:40:38.840
You're right.

00:40:42.110 --> 00:40:43.510
This whole thing is wrong.

00:40:46.710 --> 00:40:48.190
Emotional testing

00:40:48.190 --> 00:40:49.320
should never have existed.

00:40:53.110 --> 00:40:54.280
I was too naive.

